data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. NO FLOOD INSURANCE // NO HOA // NO CDD // NOW PRICED UNDER $350,000    Welcome home to 2096 Valencia Way! This lovely 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom single-family home in Clearwater/Largo is nestled at the end of a quiet dead-end street. Open-concept living with loads of natural light from every room. Freshly painted interior and exterior. 3rd bedroom has a private entrance, making it ideal as a home office, game room, or entertaining space.     Short-term (and long-term) rentals ok, as this home is in the Largo tax district. No HOA or deed restrictions coupled with the large side yards make this property ideal to store your boat, jetski, RV, or other large toys and save on storage fees!    The property has plenty of space to add-on to the home as you grow. The oversized lot has ample room to add a pool, build additional living space, add a 2nd bathroom – so many possibilities in the heart of Pinellas County! Great value for the neighborhood and loads of potential make this property a great opportunity for any buyer!
